= Userspace `libmath` (`usr/libmath`)
:toc: left
:icons: font
:sectlinks:

See also: link:index.html[Userspace Index], link:../kernel/sys.html[Kernel System Services]

`usr/libmath` contains the userspace math support library used by userspace programs for baseline arithmetic and helper routines.

== Summary

* Builds the userspace math library artifact.
* Exposes simple numeric helpers for program-level use.
* Serves as an example userspace library integrated into the image.

